            <a class="article-link" href="https://www.ft.dk/samling/20191/lovforslag/l190/index.htm">
                <span class="article-link-icon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
                <span class="article-link-text">L&#230;s lovforslaget, der udm&#248;nter aftalen (vedtaget 20. maj)</span>
            </a>

